title: AMD is slowing down at the worst possible time
description: AMD has been dominating the booming handheld gaming market, but it looks like it might give Intel a lot of room to take over.

title: Apple quietly retires one of its Apple Music tiers
description: Apple is retiring its Voice plan for Apple Music that lets people use Siri to select tracks for $5 a month – less than half the cost of the regular plan.
